PageInfo.Message:
All quests have a <COL ffdc78>"Recommended
Level".</COL>
This will tell you the level of enemies that
appear in the quest area.
<COL ffdc78>Note that the recommended level not
only
means your vocation level but also your equipment
level.</COL>
Be sure to challenge quests that match your level.

In "World Quests" and "Main Quests",
all party memebers, be them friends or pawns,
should also clear the "Recommended Level".
If your equipment does not match your level, the
quest
difficulty goes up. Be sure to be prepared!
